snippet.title: Holiday Party: Mascot Brawl Trailer
snippet.description: Get ready to laugh and play in Holiday Party: Mascot Brawl! Join the fun with your friends as silly mascot characters in crazy holiday levels. Knock your friends off the stage or dodge tricky obstacles to win. With surprise mini-games, it's a blast for everyone!
